            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Whilst the sauce is cooking, add your <strong>flaked almonds</strong> to a baking tray and put the tray in the oven for 2-3 min or until lightly toasted</p><p>Tip: Watch them like a hawk to make sure they don’t burn!</p>",
      "order": 6,
