            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the sauce has thickened, stir the <strong>roasted cauliflower</strong> through the korma sauce – this is your<strong> roasted cauliflower korma</strong></p><p>Once the rice is done, discard the <strong>cloves</strong></p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
